Articles.Content:
I was messing around with KAX and BD Armory today, and all of the sudden, I noticed that 3 major parts of the mod were gone. I installed no mods, made no modifications to the game files. They just disappeared. The parts and files are still in their respective folders, but the logs say otherwise. First thing I noticed was this:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3IAO4S0FQdgY0paUXNhaUhhSDQ/view?usp=sharing


Edited January 11, 2015 by YourEverydayWaffle
Anybody? After multiple restarts, nothing has changed. Not surprised, though.

BUMP

Ok had the same problem, figured it out:). Those specific parts have an incorrect part file. They're named "part .cfg" instead of "part.cfg". Get rid of the space. Files are in gamedata/bdarmory/parts/(bombname)
